<T>__{cut to:}
<A>__{split screen. on one side of the frame, we see captain sharp, scout master ward, and becky. on the other side, we see a seventy five year old man with a grizzled face sitting at a kitchen table drinking coffee and smoking a cigarette while a white haired woman ices a cake in the background. they are mr. and mrs. billingsley. mr. billingsley says into his}
<T>__{telephone:}
